text: An essential part of the Jamie Hyneman mindset is sitting in a library room and making long lists mapping out your potential options in terms of plans, possibilities, etc. before making any move. The other part is disappearing in the wilderness unexpectedly for months at a time.

Reminder: When you have a girlfriend, "other women" will manifest, like fish out of mud or mice of grain, to try and seduce you away, but that is merely God testing your loyalty: and if you fail, He breaks both of your legs and your pelvis and your ribcage and pierces your lungs.
